Pre-Game Insights: Gambia are the more experienced side and have several attacking options that can challenge Comoros.
Comoros and Gambia are playing each other for the first time in all competitions.
Gambia's Yankubah Minteh is looking to score in his third consecutive game, having scored against Seychelles and Gabon.
This is Comoros' second attempt to reach the AFCON finals, following their debut in 2021.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match is taking place in Morocco.
Gambia have won just once in their five official games this year, a 5-1 victory over Seychelles in a World Cup qualifier.
